Constructor that accepts adjective satellite synset properties.

Parameters:
definition - Short description / definition of the meaning.
examples - Examples of how the synset is used.
senseKeys - Keys of word senses associated with this synset.
pointers - Pointers to unresolved relationships.
lexFile - Lexical file that contains the synset.
offset - Byte offset into the data file where synset is defined.
positions - Positions that the words in this synset can occupy.
